📢 Narrator BOT 04-Mar-22 05:02 PM
The day feels like any other. The only difference was that Olwen was absent from the office the whole day, supposedly taking a day off for today’s mission. She trusted you all enough to navigate to the given address on time without having to be chaperoned. Upon reaching the gates of the large estate, guards stop you in your chosen mode of transport and ask for your details. Simply letting them know that Olwen was expecting you didn’t seem to deter them from making you cough up a valid form of identification. Those who drove here were guided to the small parking lot in front of the building where a few vintage cars were parked nicely in their boxes.
Eventually, you are ushered to the main entrance of the small mansion. A young blonde woman awaited all of you. She had been told to only allow everyone in once all 6 of you were here after all.
